25|$|A single-payer {{health system}} {{establishes}} one health <b>risk</b> <b>pool</b> {{consisting of the}} entire population of a geographic or political region. It also establishes one set of rules for services offered, reimbursement rates, drug prices, and minimum standards for required services.|$|R
